Matthew de Grood: 2014 Calgary Stabbing Victims Were Illuminati, Vampires and Werewolves
Published April 10, 2020 by Christopher di Armani
Filed Under: Canadian Mass Murders, Crime, Human Depravity
This is part of my ongoing series on Canadian Mass Murders.
This lengthy report is broken down into the following sections:
